LossData.text: Tell us what you want to acheive and receive personalized goals.
Learn about the foods you’re eating and keep your calories within your daily budget.
Reach your goals and continue to set new ones for a happier, healthier you!

Slider1.Title: Water Tracking
Slider1.Desc: Track your water intake to make sure you're getting the recommended amount daily.

Slider1.Title: Macro Tracking
Slider1.Desc: Set personalized macronutrient goals to ensure you’re getting enough protein, carbs, and more.

Slider1.Title: Device Integration
Slider1.Desc: Connect Apple Health and Google Fit for easy exercise tracking.

Slider1.Title: Patterns & Reports
Slider1.Desc: Get reports on your behaviors and progress straight to your inbox.

Slider1.Title: Scanner Feature
Slider1.Desc: Use your camera to scan package barcodes for quick tracking or create new foods with the nutrition label auto-fill.

Slider1.Title: Smart Camera
Slider1.Desc: Use your camera to take a picture of your food and allow Lose It! technology to help you log it.
